'''Douglas R. Worsnop''' is an [[United States|American]] [[atmospheric sciences|atmosphere]] and hydrospheric scientist, a significant figure in his field, currently at [[Aerodyne Research]] and an Elected Fellow of the [[American Association for the Advancement of Science]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.aaas.org/fellow/worsnop-doug |title=Doug Worsnop |publisher=aaas.org |accessdate=April 24, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aerodyne.com/employees/douglas-r-worsnop |title=Douglas Worsnop |publisher=aerodyne.com |accessdate=April 24, 2017}}</ref>

