This is a '''list of [[Genus|genera]] in the [[green algae]] [[Class (biology)|class]] [[Trebouxiophyceae]]''', sub-divided by [[Order (biology)|order]] and [[Family (biology)|family]].<ref>{{AlgaeBase taxon|name=Trebouxiophyceae |id=4356}}</ref> Some genera have uncertain [[Taxonomy (biology)|taxonomic]] placement and are listed as ''[[incertae sedis]]''. Ranks without accepted subordinate taxa have been omitted. The list is based on the data available in [[AlgaeBase]], the [[Integrated Taxonomic Information System]] (ITIS), the [[National Center for Biotechnology Information]] taxonomic database (NCBI), and other taxonomic databases.
== Order [[Chlorellales]] == {{Div col|colwidth=15em}} *Family [[Chlorellaceae]]<ref>{{AlgaeBase taxon|name=Chlorellaceae|id=4961}}</ref> ** ''[[Acanthosphaera]]'' ** ''[[Actinastrum]]'' ** ''[[Apatococcus]]'' ** ''[[Apodococcus]]'' ** ''[[Auxenochlorella]]'' ** ''[[Carolibrandtia]]'' ** ''[[Catena]]'' ** ''[[Chlorella]]'' ** ''[[Chloroparva]]'' ** ''[[Closteriopsis]]'' ** ''[[Compactochlorella]]'' ** ''[[Coronacoccus]]'' ** ''[[Coronastrum]]'' ** ''[[Cylindrocelis]]'' ** ''[[Dicellula]]'' ** ''[[Dictyosphaerium]]'' ** ''[[Didymogenes]]'' ** ''[[Fissuricella]]'' ** ''[[Follicularia]]'' ** ''[[Geminella (alga)|Geminella]]'' ** ''[[Gloeotila]]'' ** ''[[Golenkiniopsis]]'' ** ''[[Hegewaldia]]'' ** ''[[Helicosporidium]]'' ** ''[[Heynigia]]'' ** ''[[Hindakia]]'' ** ''[[Hormospora]]'' ** ''[[Kalenjinia]]'' ** ''[[Keratococcus]]'' ** ''[[Leptochlorella]]'' ** ''[[Marasphaerium]]'' ** ''[[Marinichlorella]]'' ** ''[[Marvania]]'' ** ''[[Masaia]]'' ** ''[[Meyerella]]'' ** ''[[Micractinium]]'' ** ''[[Mucidosphaerium]]'' ** ''[[Muriella]]'' ** ''[[Nannochloris]]'' ** ''[[Nanochlorum]]'' ** ''[[Palmellochaete]]'' ** ''[[Parachlorella]]'' ** ''[[Planktochlorella]]'' ** ''[[Podohedra]]'' ** ''[[Prototheca]]'' ** ''[[Pseudochloris]]'' ** ''[[Pseudosiderocelopsis]]'' ** ''[[Pumiliosphaera]]'' ** ''[[Siderocelis]]'' ** ''[[Zoochlorella]]''
